"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua_summoned"	"恶魔召唤[选技生存版]"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_enigma_demonic_conversion_lua_summoned_Description"	"通过击杀敌人来升级。"
